Document: AcceptDialog  
Path: godot/classes/class_acceptdialog.rst  
Summary: AcceptDialog allows customizing dialog actions via confirmed/canceled signals and button addition, with visibility controlled through Window popup methods.  

The default use of AcceptDialog is to allow it to only be accepted or closed, with the same result. However, the confirmed and canceled signals allow making the two actions different, and the add_button() method allows adding custom buttons and actions. Note: AcceptDialog is invisible by default. To make it visible, call one of the popup_* methods from Window on the node, such as Window.popup_centered_clamped().
---CHUNK---
Document: AcceptDialog  
Path: godot/classes/class_acceptdialog.rst  
Summary: Class properties and their default values, including overrides from the Window class.  

Property: dialog_autowrap (bool): Controls automatic text wrapping in the dialog. Default: false.  
Property: dialog_close_on_escape (bool): Closes the dialog when the escape key is pressed. Default: true.  
Property: dialog_hide_on_ok (bool): Hides the dialog after clicking "OK". Default: true.  
Property: dialog_text (String): Main text displayed in the dialog. Default: empty string.  
Property: exclusive (bool): Makes the dialog exclusive (no other windows interactable). Overrides Window's exclusive property. Default: true.  
Property: keep_title_visible (bool): Ensures the title remains visible. Overrides Window's keep_title_visible property. Default: true.  
Property: maximize_disabled (bool): Disables maximize button. Overrides Window's maximize_disabled property. Default: true.  
Property: minimize_disabled (bool): Disables minimize button. Overrides Window's minimize_disabled property. Default: true.  
Property: ok_button_text (String): Custom text for the "OK" button. Default: empty string.  
Property: title (String): Dialog title. Overrides Window's title property. Default: "Alert!".  
Property: transient (bool): Makes the dialog transient (not shown in taskbars). Overrides Window's transient property. Default: true.  
Property: visible (bool): Initial visibility state. Overrides Window's visible property. Default: false.  
Property: wrap_controls (bool): Wraps child controls to fit the dialog width. Overrides Window's wrap_controls property. Default: true.
